dmca.title: [ABUSE] Website Fraud - Abuse
dmca.body:
To Whom It May Concern:

Please note that below-referenced copyright infringement notice does not
substantially comply with the required notification elements of the Digital
Millennium Copyright Act of 1998 ("DMCA").

Please note that we have not passed on the substantive merits of your claim.

Please visit our web site at www.theplanet.com/legal.
 
Legal Response Team
THEPLANET.COM INTERNET SERVICES, INC.

-----Original Message-----
From: abuseadm@theplanet.com [mailto:abuseadm@theplanet.com] On Behalf Of
Policy Enforcement
Sent: Thursday, April 06, 2006 2:02 PM
To: DMCA
Subject: [Fwd: [ABUSE] Website Fraud - Abuse]

-----BEGIN PGP SIGNED MESSAGE-----
Hash: SHA1

For your review.
- --
Policy Enforcement
The Planet Internet Services, Inc.
http://www.theplanet.com/legal/

- -------- Original Message --------
Subject:         [ABUSE] Website Fraud - Abuse
Date:         Thu, 6 Apr 2006 03:25:54 -0700
From:         Tiffany Bass Bukow: MsMoney.com / Thrive Media <tiffany@msmoney.com>
Reply-To:         tiffany@msmoney.com
Organization:         MsMoney.com
To:         <abuse@theplanet.com>





The network solutions website states that you provided the registration
service for this domain.



Since this domain name is in violation of copyright law by taking an exact
replica of the www.msmoney.com website: version February 2005, and it
contains over 500 copyrighted MsMoney.com Inc. articles, we would like you
to assist us to remove it immediately from the internet.



Thank you,

Tiffany Bass Bukow

CEO

MsMoney.com Inc.

www.msmoney.com

717 Market St, 6th Floor

San Francisco, CA 94103

415-710-2322
